2. MENU
<details>
  <summary>View Table</summary>
	The menu table maps the product_id to the actual product_name and price of each menu item.
	| product_id	| product_name |	price |
	| --- 	| ---  | --- |
	| 1 |	price |	10 |
	| 2 |	curry |	15 |
	| 3 |	ramen |	12 |
	
</details>


3. MEMBERS
<details>
  <summary>View Table</summary>
